to talk to you about Regina.

27:48.388 --> 27:50.422
Is everything okay?

27:52.292 --> 27:54.529
When you guys are together, do you...

27:54.563 --> 27:57.267
well, has she...

27:57.302 --> 27:59.170
ever had a drink?

27:59.204 --> 28:02.107
You mean like a glass of wine or something?

28:02.142 --> 28:05.177
- Yeah.
- Yeah, why?

28:08.181 --> 28:10.182
Regina's an alcoholic.

28:12.552 --> 28:15.220
And she didn't tell you.

28:15.255 --> 28:16.489
No.

28:25.065 --> 28:26.466
No.

28:32.440 --> 28:34.975
Do you need a ride home or something?

28:35.009 --> 28:36.209
No, it's okay.

28:36.244 --> 28:38.445
Uh, thanks.

28:44.119 --> 28:47.221
"You say that the deaf
students will just 'adjust, '

28:47.255 --> 28:50.024
but what you mean is they'll just

28:50.059 --> 28:52.060
get used to second-class status."

28:52.094 --> 28:56.999
We realize that this is
not an ideal situation.

28:57.033 --> 28:59.935
"You are compromising the
quality of their education."

28:59.969 --> 29:02.972
Have any of you ever
actually been to Carlton?

29:03.006 --> 29:05.308
We've been to every district school,

29:05.342 --> 29:09.011
and I'm sorry but we're not opening the
floor to anyone who's not on our agenda.

29:09.046 --> 29:11.981
You're making a decision that
affects over 100 deaf students,

29:12.016 --> 29:14.918
and you don't have time
to listen to one of them?

29:16.087 --> 29:17.153
Step forward.

29:24.896 --> 29:28.765
Carlton is the one place in the world

29:28.799 --> 29:31.034
where having ears that
don't work doesn't matter.

29:32.904 --> 29:35.772
It's not just a school to us,

29:35.807 --> 29:37.775
it's our home.

29:38.877 --> 29:40.878
And by letting more hearing kids in,

29:40.912 --> 29:43.080
you're saying it's okay to invade our home.

29:43.115 --> 29:44.982
But it's not.

29:53.992 --> 29:55.860
Okay.

29:55.894 --> 29:58.063
Honey, in a perfect world,

29:58.097 --> 30:01.700
we'd have money for deaf
schools and organic lunches

30:01.735 --> 30:04.737
and state-of-the-art computer
labs in all our schools.

30:04.771 --> 30:06.840
But we don't.

30:06.874 --> 30:09.909
We're stretched incredibly thin these days.

30:09.944 --> 30:14.013
You found money to hire the college
football coach at Jefferson...

30:14.048 --> 30:17.750
 ... And resurface the track at Taft.

30:18.986 --> 30:21.888
I guess it just comes
down to how you prioritize.

30:40.574 --> 30:42.575
