31:18.479 --> 31:20.514
We see how well that's working out.

31:22.616 --> 31:26.685
- Hey, how much was all this?
- No, please, don't worry about it.

31:26.720 --> 31:29.655
- No, come on, please.
- I put it on my mom's card. It's fine, stop.

31:29.689 --> 31:32.324
It's on the house...

31:32.358 --> 31:34.526
Patricia Sawyer's house that is.

31:39.265 --> 31:43.302
Are you saving up for all
your travels and stuff or...

31:43.337 --> 31:46.640
If by "saving up" you mean "the
occasional A.T.M. withdrawal

31:46.674 --> 31:50.443
because my mom hasn't changed
her pin since 2004," then yes.

31:50.478 --> 31:53.146
Yes. What? Don't... come on.

31:53.180 --> 31:55.415
Don't give me that look.
I've seen your house.

31:55.450 --> 31:59.086
Don't pretend like you
don't also dip into the well,

31:59.120 --> 32:01.388
- if you know what I mean.
- Well, I mean, I've...

32:01.423 --> 32:04.157
definitely done my fair
share of stupid stuff,

32:04.192 --> 32:06.193
but, you know,

32:06.228 --> 32:08.196
I've never taken from them.

32:08.230 --> 32:10.532
It's just compensation

32:10.566 --> 32:13.235
for emotional abuse.

32:18.106 --> 32:21.042
I'm sorry I missed rehearsal yesterday.

32:21.076 --> 32:23.244
Yeah, I heard about the meeting.

32:23.278 --> 32:25.446
Is everything okay?

32:25.480 --> 32:28.315
I don't know. The school
board's voting today

32:28.349 --> 32:30.251
for what happens next year.

32:30.285 --> 32:35.256
Hmm, whether I stay or go.

32:36.392 --> 32:39.160
It's okay. I get it, you know.

32:39.195 --> 32:43.030
You don't want the Replicants taking over.

32:43.065 --> 32:45.433
