back? Telling him I'm a drunk?

35:29.568 --> 35:31.336
- I didn't tell him that.
- Why didn't you come to me?

35:31.370 --> 35:34.339
- Because I wasn't sure so...
- So you decided to ruin

35:34.373 --> 35:37.575
