otherwise crappy life right now?

35:37.610 --> 35:39.511
- I was just trying to help.
- Help?

35:39.545 --> 35:42.346
Who the hell do you think
you are? You don't know me.

35:42.381 --> 35:44.548
- I'm sorry, Regina...
- Who else did you tell?

35:44.583 --> 35:47.218
- Daphne? Your parents?
- No.

35:47.252 --> 35:49.420
- Did you call my mom in Puerto Rico?
- No.

35:49.455 --> 35:52.123
Stay out of my business, okay?

35:52.157 --> 35:54.159
You stay out of it.

36:18.546 --> 36:20.347
