36:38.429 --> 36:40.162
Really.

36:41.331 --> 36:44.199
They're not expanding the hearing program.

36:44.233 --> 36:47.334
- They're not?
- No.

36:50.270 --> 36:52.237
They're closing Carlton.

36:52.271 --> 36:55.073
What do you mean they're closing it?

36:55.107 --> 36:58.075
The school board voted

36:58.109 --> 37:02.113
to sell the property and
shut down Carlton for good.

37:02.147 --> 37:04.382
They're going to separate us

37:04.416 --> 37:09.054
- and send us to different schools next year.
- Oh no.

37:09.088 --> 37:11.256
I'm so sorry, honey.

37:12.458 --> 37:15.026
I'm sorry.

37:21.300 --> 37:24.300
Go away.

37:30.074 --> 37:32.475
- Bay?
- I said go away.

37:35.378 --> 37:37.379
You told me to stay out of your life.

37:37.413 --> 37:39.481
Why don't you try staying out of mine?

37:41.150 --> 37:44.185
Bay, I am so sorry.

37:44.219 --> 37:46.454
And I am so touched

37:46.488 --> 37:48.456
that you wanted to help me.

37:51.393 --> 37:54.295
Well, you should have a sit
down with an-hour-ago-Regina,

37:54.330 --> 37:56.264
because she seemed pretty pissed.

37:58.067 --> 38:00.034
I was busy seeing myself as a victim,

38:00.069 --> 38:01.402
so I would have an excuse...

38:01.437 --> 38:03.237
to keep drinking.

38:03.272 --> 38:06.240
So you are drinking again?

38:06.275 --> 38:08.376
Yes.

38:08.410 --> 38:11.079
And it's embarrassing and humiliating

38:11.113 --> 38:13.081
- and I took it all out on you.
- Why?

38:13.115 --> 38:14.416
I'm on your side.

38:16.352 --> 38:18.320
Ever since we moved in,

38:18.354 --> 38:21.089
I have had to depend on other people.

38:21.124 --> 38:23.025
Your mom got me the job at Geraldo's,

38:23.059 --> 38:24.459
Angelo was going to finance the salon

38:24.494 --> 38:27.062
and now when I talk to Daphne

38:27.096 --> 38:29.397
I feel like I need an interpreter.

38:29.432 --> 38:32.200
And drinking makes that
all a little easier.

38:35.271 --> 38:37.439
At least for a little while.

38:37.473 --> 38:39.374
And then you sober up,

38:39.409 --> 38:42.044
and you hate yourself for doing it,

38:42.078 --> 38:44.280
so you want to feel okay again.

38:44.314 --> 38:47.083
- So...
- You drink again.

38:47.117 --> 38:49.252
Pretty much.

38:52.190 --> 38:54.124
So what happens now?

38:56.060 --> 38:58.462
I get myself to the
next meeting I can find.

38:58.496 --> 39:01.465
And I call my sponsor and I
start working the program again,

39:01.500 --> 39:04.201
one day at a time.

39:04.235 --> 39:08.071
Well, is there anything
I can do to help you?

39:10.507 --> 39:12.275
Try to forgive me?

39:15.245 --> 39:17.113
I can do that.

39:19.316 --> 39:21.284
Thank you.

39:27.491 --> 39:29.425
Is, uh... 

39:29.460 --> 39:33.063
there any way that we
could keep this between us?

39:33.097 --> 39:37.034
I don't want to worry Daphne, and
if John and Kathryn found out...

39:37.068 --> 39:38.168
I won't say anything.

39:38.202 --> 39:40.170
Thank you.

39:42.273 --> 39:44.374
This is done, Bay.

39:44.409 --> 39:46.143
You have my word.

40:06.098 --> 40:08.366
I was beginning to think
you weren't gonna come.

40:08.400 --> 40:10.535
I almost didn't.

40:12.471 --> 40:15.306
I'm not sure that this is a good idea.

40:16.375 --> 40:18.342
I am.

40:20.379 --> 40:23.114
I meant what I said on Valentine's Day.

40:23.149 --> 40:26.185
We're just too different.

40:26.219 --> 40:29.121
That's why I didn't text you back.

40:31.224 --> 40:34.193
I meant what I said on
Valentine's day, too.

40:36.263 --> 40:40.366
I've never told anybody
"I love you" before.

40:43.170 --> 40:46.139
You make me want to be a better person,

40:46.173 --> 40:49.344
- someone that you deserve to be with.
- Toby...

40:49.378 --> 40:52.347
And you were the one who said

40:52.382 --> 40:55.317
that having faith isn't easy.

40:55.351 --> 40:57.486
It's believing in something

40:57.520 --> 41:01.056
even when reason tells you not to, right?

41:04.127 --> 41:05.327
Right.

41:05.361 --> 41:09.098
Well, I have faith in us.

41:11.134 --> 41:14.269
